query.sfwSql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND STATUS_VALUE='ACTV'
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND ORG_TYPE_VALUE='EMPL' AND STATUS_VALUE='ACTV'

SELECT PA.PERSON_ID as PERSON_ID, PE.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID as PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID as PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, PA.START_DATE AS PLAN_START_DATE, PA.END_DATE AS PLAN_END_DATE, LATEST_PAPIT_START_DATE, LATEST_PAPIT_END_DATE, P.LAST_NAME as LAST_NAME , P.FIRST_NAME as FIRST_NAME, PL.PLAN_NAME as PLAN_NAME, CV.[DESCRIPTION] AS PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS, 'Payment election as pension check but no deduction for the month' as ERR_MSG FROM (SELECT PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION WHERE PAYMENT_METHOD_VALUE = 'PNCH' AND (ISNULL(IBS_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' OR ISNULL(IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_FLAG,'N') ='Y') AND PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL ) PE INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA ON PE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON P ON PA.PERSON_ID = P.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_ID = CV.CODE_ID AND PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE INNER JOIN ( SELECT CV.PLAN_ID,PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM ( --SELECT DATA1 AS ITEM_CODE, -- CAST(DATA2 AS INT) AS PLAN_ID -- FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = 1711
--UNION ALL
SELECT DATA2 AS ITEM_CODE, CAST(DATA1 AS INT) AS PLAN_ID FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = 1708
) CV INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON CV.ITEM_CODE = PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE ) AS INS ON PA.PLAN_ID = INS.PLAN_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL ON PA.PLAN_ID = PL.PLAN_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID , START_DATE AS LATEST_PAPIT_START_DATE, END_DATE AS LATEST_PAPIT_END_DATE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE WHERE @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN START_DATE AND ISNULL(END_DATE,'29001231') )PAPIT ON PE.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND INS.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID
WHERE PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL AND PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2'
UNION ALL
select PA.PERSON_ID, pe.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, Pa.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, PA.START_DATE AS PLAN_START_DATE, PA.END_DATE AS PLAN_END_DATE, LATEST_PAPIT_START_DATE, LATEST_PAPIT_END_DATE, P.LAST_NAME, P.FIRST_NAME, Pl.PLAN_NAME, CV.[DESCRIPTION] AS PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS, 'Pension check deduction exists ' + CASE WHEN PE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL OR ( ISNULL(PE.IBS_FLAG,'N') = 'N' AND ISNULL(PE.IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_FLAG,'N') ='N' ) THEN 'for a non-IBS member' WHEN ISNULL(PE.PAYMENT_METHOD_VALUE,'') <> 'PNCH' AND PE.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'but payment election is not pension check' WHEN pa.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID is null or pa.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE <> 'ENL2' THEN 'but member is not enrolled in plan' Else '' END as ERR_MSG from ( SELECT pac.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PAC.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID,PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID, PAPI.START_DATE AS LATEST_PAPIT_START_DATE, PAPI.END_DATE AS LATEST_PAPIT_END_DATE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPI INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PAC ON PAC.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPI.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS(NOLOCK) PAS ON PAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAC.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV1 ON PAS.STATUS_ID= CV1.CODE_ID AND PAS.STATUS_VALUE = CV1.CODE_VALUE WHERE (CV1.DATA2 = 'RECV' OR CV1.DATA2 = 'APRD' ) AND PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS1 (nolock) WHERE PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAC.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE ORDER BY PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC,PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID DESC ) AND @PAYMENTDATE BETWEEN PAPI.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAPI.END_DATE,'29001231') )PAPIT INNER JOIN ( SELECT CV.PLAN_ID,PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM ( --SELECT DATA1 AS ITEM_CODE, -- cast(DATA2 as int) AS PLAN_ID -- FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = 1711
--UNION ALL
SELECT DATA2 AS ITEM_CODE, cast(DATA1 as int) AS PLAN_ID FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = 1708
) CV INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON CV.ITEM_CODE = PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE ) AS INS on PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = INS.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON p ON PAPIT.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = P.PERSON_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT pa ON PAPIT.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = PA.PERSON_ID AND INS.PLAN_ID = PA.PLAN_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_ID = CV.CODE_ID AND PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL ON PA.PLAN_ID = PL.PLAN_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION PE ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE ( PE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL OR ( ISNULL(PE.IBS_FLAG,'N') = 'N' AND ISNULL(PE.IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_FLAG,'N') ='N' ) OR ISNULL(PE.PAYMENT_METHOD_VALUE,'') <> 'PNCH' OR PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL OR PA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE <> 'ENL2' ) and isnull(pa.END_DATE,getdate()) <> isnull(LATEST_PAPIT_END_DATE,getdate())
